            "text": "The article contains an image [1] showing several tech-company-funded fonts side-by-side.<p>The fonts have some differences, but I&#x27;d have to agree with you the changes are so subtle it&#x27;s hard to believe they resulted from an attempt to make a _radically_ new typeface.<p>[1] <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.arun.is&#x2F;blog&#x2F;custom-typefaces&#x2F;unique_typefaces_mobile.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.arun.is&#x2F;blog&#x2F;custom-typefaces&#x2F;unique_typefaces_m...</a>",
