            "text": "I&#x27;m curious if there are any lawsuits based on basically tracing &amp; duplicating fonts? Does adding the slightest accent to the letter &quot;a&quot; allow you to trace the other 99%.<p>Also many of these look like they just adjusted the weight ever so slightly. With variable fonts, I&#x27;m curious how this come into play when considering copyrights.",
