            "text": "Wow, I didn&#x27;t even realise Helvetica needed a licence. Nor that its pay per click:<p>&quot;When purchasing your digital ad license, you specify the number of impressions your campaign will require. If you’re uncertain how many impressions you will need, you can purchase a small allotment and true up at the end of the month.&quot;<p><a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.fonts.com&#x2F;font&#x2F;linotype&#x2F;helvetica&#x2F;licenses\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.fonts.com&#x2F;font&#x2F;linotype&#x2F;helvetica&#x2F;licenses</a>",
