            "by": "crispyambulance",
            "id": 18542876,
            "parent": 18542604,
            "text": "<p><pre><code>    &gt; Sorry.\n</code></pre>\nThanks, but no need for the phony apology.<p>Typefaces, like other graphic elements, might not be felt to the point of the reader explicitly &quot;recognizing&quot; these contributions. Their impact is real albeit subtle. Designers are aware of that but still work really hard anyway.",
